name: "Contemplative Creature" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Liner pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] This here little monster is my contribution to the #objekt4objekt movement, in which weirdo artists GIVE AWAY their artz to folks who enjoy collecting! I'm setting the royalties to 13%, since this piece is being released at such a miniscule cost (0.001 tez), and I'm only minting 101 pieces, cuz 101 is a prime number! Enjoy!!! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
